text: Hohenheim is a neighborhood in Stuttgart, Germany. The name can also refer to: *Hohenheim Castle *University of Hohenheim *Bombast von Hohenheim, Swabian noble family (extinct 1566) **Paracelsus, born Theophrastus von Hohenheim *Franziska von Hohenheim, for whom the Swabian name and title was revived in 1774 *Van Hohenheim, a character in the anime series and manga Fullmetal Alchemist
